        <updateDate>2008-04-01T21:17:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Foreclosure Credit Forgiveness Act of 2008 - Amends the Fair Credit Reporting Act to prohibit the foreclosure on a subprime mortgage of a consumer from being taken into account by any person preparing or calculating the consumer's credit score.</p> <p>Defines &quot;subprime mortgage&quot; as any consumer credit transaction secured by the consumer's principal dwelling that meets criteria prescribed by the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
